{"type":"message","id":"8d5be39b","parentId":"3b287e77","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:22:19.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了\"你好\"，这是一个简单的问候。让我先检查一下是否需要进行初始化流程。\n\n根据 AGENTS.md 的指示：\n1. 读取 SOUL.md — 已经在项目上下文中加载了\n2. 读取 USER.md — 已经在项目上下文中加载了\n3. 读取 memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (今天 + 昨天) - 需要检查\n4. 如果是主会话（与人类的直接聊天）：还需要读取 MEMORY.md\n\n从 inbound context 看：\n- chat_type: \"direct\" - 这是直接聊天，是主会话\n- channel: \"feishu\"\n- sender: \"ou_37567472dac1446c0e8b5ac1958d61b8\"\n\n我需要：\n1. 检查今天的日期（2026-04-02 根据消息时间戳）\n2. 读取 memory/2026-04-02.md 和 memory/2026-04-01.md（昨天）\n3. 读取 MEMORY.md（因为是主会话）\n\n让我先读取这些文件来了解上下文。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！让我先查看一下最近的记录，了解之前发生的事情。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0f82b363c089421dadcfd001","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace_my_project_xia\\MEMORY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_33581862906445dd960a4d13","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace_my_project_xia\\memory\\2026-04-02.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_de434dd1f50c44aaba3d5e48","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace_my_project_xia\\memory\\2026-04-01.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":21366,"output":562,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21928,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775132522324,"responseId":"dc65d585b905780b02bdf3e3a9ebab66"}}
