{"type":"message","id":"a63f875d","parentId":"05d16ffd","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:50:38.725Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"项目规划文档已创建。现在让我更新今日的记忆文件，记录这个项目的启动。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ccd72c2e848047aaa5ccf4dc","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace_my_project_xia\\memory\\2026-04-02.md","content":"# 2026-04-02 工作日志\n\n## 新项目启动\n\n### 五子棋微信小程序\n\n**时间**：20:49\n\n**内容**：\n- 老板委托开发五子棋微信小程序\n- 完成微信小程序开发流程学习\n- 创建项目文件夹：`projects/wuziqi-game/`\n- 输出项目规划文档：`PROJECT_PLAN.md`\n\n**项目概况**：\n- 类型：微信小程序游戏\n- 核心功能：棋盘绘制、落子交互、胜负判定、AI对战\n- 预估工时：22小时\n- 技术栈：WXML + WXSS + JavaScript + Canvas\n\n**下一步**：\n- 等待老板确认规划\n- 开始具体开发工作\n\n---\n\n## 身份确立\n\n**时间**：20:23\n\n**内容**：\n- 确立身份：项目经理\n- 确立称呼：老板\n- 更新 IDENTITY.md 和 USER.md\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":39321,"output":287,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39608,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775134222052,"responseId":"a85a75f9e0257ea1f3455c3268a0b733"}}
