{"type":"message","id":"b7a64f9f","parentId":"1354b26d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:07:16.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file structure looks correct. The game.json file exists at `miniprogram\\pages\\game\\game.json`.\n\nThe error message \"game.json: 未找到 game.json 文件\" is a bit misleading. It might be looking for something at the root level.\n\nWait, I think I see the issue. The error says it's looking for game.json, which might be a different game.json - maybe a mini-game configuration file at the project root?\n\nActually, for WeChat Mini Programs, if this is a game (小游戏), it needs a game.json at the root instead of app.json. But we're building a mini program (小程序), not a mini game (小游戏).\n\nLet me check the project.config.json to see if there's a configuration issue. Also, let me check if the user imported the correct directory.\n\nThe user should import:\n`C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace_my_project_xia\\projects\\wuziqi-game\\miniprogram`\n\nBut wait, the project.config.json should be at the root of the imported directory. Let me check its content.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"文件结构正确。问题可能是导入目录不对。让我检查一下配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4e181b63562f41848cb7dbe2","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace_my_project_xia\\projects\\wuziqi-game\\miniprogram\\project.config.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":74063,"output":504,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74567,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775142415315,"responseId":"e0218fb92fc253b7219c734ad8e31c9c"}}
