{"type":"message","id":"f22944c9","parentId":"ef638117","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:07:52.930Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The project.config.json looks correct. The `compileType` is set to \"miniprogram\" which is correct.\n\nBut the error message is strange - it says \"game.json: 未找到 game.json 文件\". This is a specific error that happens when:\n\n1. The project is configured as a mini-game (小游戏) instead of mini-program (小程序)\n2. Or there's something in the configuration that's pointing to game mode\n\nWait, I see the issue now! The `compileType` is \"miniprogram\" which is correct. But the error message about \"game.json\" at the root level suggests the compiler might be confused.\n\nActually, looking more carefully at the error message:\n```\ngame.json: 未找到 game.json 文件，或者文件读取失败\n```\n\nThis error message appears twice. This could be a WeChat DevTools issue where it's trying to find a game.json at the root for some reason.\n\nLet me check if there's a miniprogramRoot setting that needs to be configured. Also, I notice the appid is filled in with an actual appid now \"wxa973c0408827c9b5\" which is good.\n\nThe issue might be that:\n1. The user imported the wrong directory (maybe imported `wuziqi-game` instead of `wuziqi-game/miniprogram`)\n2. Or there's a configuration issue\n\nLet me ask the user to verify which directory they imported. Also, I should check if the miniprogramRoot setting is needed.\n\nActually, looking at the project structure, I should have put the project.config.json at the wuziqi-game level, not inside miniprogram. The standard WeChat Mini Program structure is:\n\n```\nproject-root/\n├── project.config.json  (at root)\n├── miniprogram/\n│   ├── app.js\n│   ├── app.json\n│   └── ...\n```\n\nBut I put project.config.json inside miniprogram folder. \n\nI need to restructure the project. The correct approach is to place project.config.json at the root level with miniprogramRoot pointing to the miniprogram folder, which is the standard WeChat Mini Program project layout.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！项目结构需要调整。\n\n微信小程序的标准结构应该是：\n```\nwuziqi-game/\n├── project.config.json    ← 在根目录\n├── miniprogram/           ← 源码目录\n│   ├── app.js\n│   ├── app.json\n│   └── ...\n```\n\n我来修正结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3ef4371c77944b54a30a1f32","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace_my_project_xia\\projects\\wuziqi-game\\project.config.json","content":"{\n  \"description\": \"五子棋小游戏项目配置文件\",\n  \"miniprogramRoot\": \"miniprogram/\",\n  \"compileType\": \"miniprogram\",\n  \"projectname\": \"wuziqi-game\",\n  \"setting\": {\n    \"urlCheck\": true,\n    \"es6\": true,\n    \"enhance\": true,\n    \"postcss\": true,\n    \"preloadBackgroundData\": false,\n    \"minified\": true,\n    \"newFeature\": false,\n    \"coverView\": true,\n    \"nodeModules\": false,\n    \"autoAudits\": false,\n    \"showShadowRootInWxmlPanel\": true,\n    \"scopeDataCheck\": false,\n    \"uglifyFileName\": false,\n    \"checkInvalidKey\": true,\n    \"checkSiteMap\": true,\n    \"uploadWithSourceMap\": true,\n    \"compileHotReLoad\": false,\n    \"useMultiFrameRuntime\": true,\n    \"useApiHook\": true,\n    \"useApiHostProcess\": true,\n    \"babelSetting\": {\n      \"ignore\": [],\n      \"disablePlugins\": [],\n      \"outputPath\": \"\"\n    },\n    \"bundle\": false,\n    \"useIsolateContext\": true,\n    \"userConfirmedBundleSwitch\": false,\n    \"packNpmManually\": false,\n    \"packNpmRelationList\": [],\n    \"minifyWXSS\": true,\n    \"showES6CompileOption\": false\n  },\n  \"appid\": \"请替换为你的AppID\",\n  \"libVersion\": \"3.3.4\",\n  \"condition\": {}\n}\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a47c4bfb653e46fda8733521","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Remove-Item -Path \"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace_my_project_xia\\projects\\wuziqi-game\\miniprogram\\project.config.json\" -Force"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"