{"type":"message","id":"b69b16cb","parentId":"1ca13252","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:08:10.628Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've moved the project.config.json to the root level and added `miniprogramRoot: \"miniprogram/\"` to point to the source directory. Now I need to tell the user to re-import the project.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已修正。现在请重新导入项目：\n\n---\n\n## 重新导入步骤\n\n### 步骤1：关闭当前项目\n\n在开发者工具中，点击左上角「项目」→「关闭项目」\n\n### 步骤2：重新导入\n\n1. 点击「导入项目」\n2. **目录选择**：\n   ```\n   C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace_my_project_xia\\projects\\wuziqi-game\n   ```\n   ⚠️ 注意：是 `wuziqi-game` 这个文件夹，不是里面的 `miniprogram`\n\n3. AppID：选择「测试号」或输入你的AppID\n4. 点击「导入」\n\n### 步骤3：重新编译\n\n按 **Ctrl+B** 编译\n\n---\n\n**正确导入后，目录结构应该是：**\n\n```\nwuziqi-game/              ← 导入这个目录\n├── project.config.json   ← 根目录配置\n├── miniprogram/          ← 源码\n│   ├── app.js\n│   ├── app.json\n│   └── pages/\n└── docs/\n```\n\n老板，请按以上步骤重新导入后再试。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":75835,"output":346,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76181,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775142473258,"responseId":"8f10af7496521c084803b61e887ce2af"}}
