{"type":"message","id":"a6206f9d","parentId":"ff454768","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:40:47.659Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在需要添加音效文件。我需要创建一个audio目录，并使用一个base64编码的简单音效，或者使用微信小程序自带的振动反馈作为替代方案。\n\n由于我无法直接创建音频文件，我有几个选择：\n1. 使用微信小程序的振动反馈 `wx.vibrateShort()` 作为落子反馈\n2. 使用在线音效URL\n3. 让用户自己添加音效文件\n\n最好的方案是使用振动反馈，这样不需要额外的文件，同时提供良好的触感反馈。让我修改代码使用振动反馈。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在让我修改代码使用振动反馈作为落子音效（不需要额外文件）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a93ef803253b4054a347139c","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\WeChatProjects\\wuziqi-game\\miniprogram\\pages\\game\\game.js","oldText":"  // 初始化音频\n  initAudio() {\n    try {\n      clickAudioContext = wx.createInnerAudioContext()\n      clickAudioContext.src = '/audio/click.mp3'\n    } catch (e) {\n      console.log('音频初始化失败', e)\n    }\n  },\n\n  // 播放落子音效\n  playClickSound() {\n    if (clickAudioContext) {\n      try {\n        clickAudioContext.stop()\n        clickAudioContext.play()\n      } catch (e) {\n        console.log('播放音效失败', e)\n      }\n    }\n  },","newText":"  // 播放落子音效和振动\n  playClickSound() {\n    // 振动反馈\n    try {\n      wx.vibrateShort({ type: 'light' })\n    } catch (e) {\n      console.log('振动失败', e)\n    }\n  },"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":103121,"output":476,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103597,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775144428000,"responseId":"5580a19f0a4f650150977e1933b694b8"}}
