{"type":"message","id":"b88fd280","parentId":"f460847b","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:41:30.111Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要修改wxss文件，确保board-container有正确的样式。让我检查一下并确保样式正确。\n\n之前我看到board-container的样式是：\n```css\n.board-container {\n  flex: 1;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  padding: 20rpx;\n  min-height: 0;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.chess-board {\n  width: 680rpx;\n  height: 680rpx;\n  ...\n}\n```\n\n问题可能是：\n1. Canvas使用了动态style，但wxss中也设置了width/height，可能冲突\n2. board-container的flex:1可能导致高度计算问题\n\n让我修改样式，确保Canvas能正确显示。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_832b7d746bad437dbf1839a0","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/* game.wxss - 游戏页面样式（修复版） */\n\npage {\n  height: 100%;\n  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);\n}\n\n.game-container {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  height: 100vh;\n  padding: 0;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\n/* 顶部信息栏 */\n.header {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 20rpx 32rpx;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n\n.player-card {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 12rpx 20rpx;\n  border-radius: 16rpx;\n  transition: all 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.player-card.active {\n  background: rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.15);\n  box-shadow: 0 0 20rpx rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.2);\n}\n\n.chess-icon {\n  width: 48rpx;\n  height: 48rpx;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  margin-right: 12rpx;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n\n.player-card .chess-icon:last-child {\n  margin-right: 0;\n  margin-left: 12rpx;\n}\n\n.chess-icon.black {\n  background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #4a4a4a, #0a0a0a);\n  box-shadow: 0 4rpx 12rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n}\n\n.chess-icon.white {\n  background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #ffffff, #d0d0d0);\n  box-shadow: 0 4rpx 12rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n}\n\n.player-info {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n}\n\n.player-info.right {\n  align-items: flex-end;\n}\n\n.player-name {\n  font-size: 26rpx;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  color: #ffffff;\n}\n\n.player-label {\n  font-size: 20rpx;\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);\n  margin-top: 2rpx;\n}\n\n.vs-badge {\n  padding: 6rpx 20rpx;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  border-radius: 20rpx;\n}\n\n.vs-badge text {\n  font-size: 22rpx;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n}\n\n/* 状态栏 */\n.status-bar {\n  padding: 12rpx 0;\n  text-align: center;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n\n.status-text {\n  font-size: 26rpx;\n  color: #e94560;\n  font-weight: 500;\n}\n\n/* 棋盘区域 */\n.board-container {\n  flex: 1;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  padding: 20rpx;\n  min-height: 0;\n}\n\n/* Canvas样式 */\n.chess-board {\n  display: block;\n  border-radius: 8rpx;\n  box-shadow: 0 10rpx 40rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n}\n\n/* 操作按钮栏 */\n.action-bar {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 24rpx;\n  padding: 20rpx 32rpx;\n  padding-bottom: calc(20rpx + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));\n  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n\n.action-btn {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  padding: 16rpx 28rpx;\n  border-radius: 16rpx;\n  min-width: 120rpx;\n  transition: all 0.2s ease;\n}\n\n.action-btn:active {\n  transform: scale(0.95);\n}\n\n.action-btn.primary {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560 0%, #ff6b6b 100%);\n  box-shadow: 0 8rpx 24rpx rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.3);\n}\n\n.action-btn.secondary {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  border: 1rpx solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n}\n\n.btn-icon {\n  font-size: 32rpx;\n  margin-bottom: 4rpx;\n}\n\n.btn-text {\n  font-size: 22rpx;\n  color: #ffffff;\n}\n\n/* 结果弹窗 */\n.result-modal {\n  position: fixed;\n  top: 0;\n  left: 0;\n  right: 0;\n  bottom: 0;\n  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  z-index: 1000;\n}\n\n.result-content {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 48rpx 64rpx;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n  border-radius: 32rpx;\n  box-shadow: 0 40rpx 100rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);\n  border: 2rpx solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  animation: modalIn 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n@keyframes modalIn {\n  from {\n    opacity: 0;\n    transform: scale(0.9);\n  }\n  to {\n    opacity: 1;\n    transform: scale(1);\n  }\n}\n\n.result-icon {\n  font-size: 100rpx;\n  margin-bottom: 20rpx;\n}\n\n.result-icon.black-win {\n  text-shadow: 0 0 40rpx rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);\n}\n\n.result-icon.white-win {\n  text-shadow: 0 0 40rpx rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);\n}\n\n.result-title {\n  font-size: 44rpx;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  color: #ffffff;\n  margin-bottom: 10rpx;\n}\n\n.result-subtitle {\n  font-size: 26rpx;\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n  margin-bottom: 32rpx;\n}\n\n.result-actions {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 16rpx;\n  width: 100%;\n}\n\n.result-btn {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 80rpx;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  border-radius: 40rpx;\n  font-size: 28rpx;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  transition: all 0.2s ease;\n}\n\n.result-btn:active {\n  transform: scale(0.98);\n}\n\n.result-btn.primary {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e94560 0%, #ff6b6b 100%);\n  color: #ffffff;\n}\n\n.result-btn.secondary {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  color: #ffffff;\n  border: 1rpx solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n}\n","path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\WeChatProjects\\wuziqi-game\\miniprogram\\pages\\game\\game.wxss"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":103520,"output":2081,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105601,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","t