{"type":"message","id":"49b0bfe3","parentId":"a1e74ca6","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:46:24.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"代码已重写，主要改进：\n1. 简化了Canvas初始化逻辑\n2. 使用bindtap代替touchstart/touchend\n3. 禁用了页面滚动（page设置overflow: hidden）\n4. 使用disable-scroll属性防止Canvas滚动\n5. 简化了布局和样式\n\n让我更新记忆。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"老板，已彻底重写代码。请按 **Ctrl+B** 重新编译。\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 修复内容\n\n| 问题 | 解决方案 |\n|------|----------|\n| 看不到棋盘 | 简化Canvas初始化，使用同步API |\n| 无法落子 | 改用 `bindtap` 事件，简化坐标计算 |\n| 界面缩放 | 页面禁用滚动，Canvas禁用滚动 |\n\n---\n\n## 主要改动\n\n1. **简化Canvas**：直接计算尺寸，减少异步嵌套\n2. **简化事件**：用 `bindtap` 替代 `touchstart/touchend`\n3. **禁用滚动**：\n   - `page { overflow: hidden }`\n   - `canvas { disable-scroll: true }`\n4. **简化布局**：减少嵌套层级\n\n---\n\n**请重新编译测试，如果还有问题告诉我控制台的错误信息。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":108982,"output":332,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109314,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775144767530,"responseId":"0dd2270658f0b566de68cb01294e0105"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6bf7c039","parentId":"49b0bfe3","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:49:31.657Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-02 23:49 GMT+8] 还有问题：\n1. 点击人机对战进入到游戏页面时，先出现棋盘，在切屏幕，二者不同步\n2. 棋盘出现了，但是个长方形的，网格不是正方形分布\n3. 无法落子"}],"timestamp":1775144971643}}
{"type":"message","id":"9882d0fd","parentId":"6bf7c039","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:50:46.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户反馈的问题：\n1. 屏幕切换时棋盘和画布不同步\n2. 棋盘是长方形，网格不是正方形\n3. 无法落子\n\n这些问题可能是因为：\n1. Canvas初始化时机问题\n2. Canvas宽高设置问题 - 需要确保宽高一致\n3. 点击事件坐标计算问题\n\n让我重新设计Canvas，确保：\n1. Canvas是正方形\n2. 网格是正方形\n3. 点击坐标正确计算\n\n关键是要确保Canvas的实际像素尺寸和CSS尺寸一致，并且在初始化时正确设置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"老板，让我彻底重构Canvas逻辑，使用更可靠的方式。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a5d97d1294c846e6be114828","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"<!--game.wxml - 游戏页面 -->\n<view class=\"game-container\">\n  <!-- 顶部 -->\n  <view class=\"header\">\n    <view class=\"player {{currentPlayer === 1 ? 'active' : ''}}\">\n      <view class=\"chess black\"></view>\n      <text>{{player1Name}}</text>\n    </view>\n    <text class=\"vs\">VS</text>\n    <view class=\"player {{currentPlayer === 2 ? 'active' : ''}}\">\n      <text>{{player2Name}}</text>\n      <view class=\"chess white\"></view>\n    </view>\n  </view>\n  \n  <view class=\"status\">{{statusText}}</view>\n\n  <!-- 棋盘 - 使用固定尺寸 -->\n  <view class=\"board-box\">\n    <view class=\"board-frame\" style=\"width: {{boardPx}}px; height: {{boardPx}}px;\">\n      <canvas \n        type=\"2d\"\n        id=\"board\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\"\n        bindtap=\"handleTap\"\n      ></canvas>\n    </view>\n  </view>\n\n  <!-- 按钮 -->\n  <view class=\"actions\">\n    <button class=\"btn\" bindtap=\"undo\" disabled=\"{{!canUndo}}\">悔棋</button>\n    <button class=\"btn primary\" bindtap=\"restart\">重开</button>\n    <button class=\"btn\" bindtap=\"goBack\">返回</button>\n  </view>\n</view>\n\n<!-- 结果弹窗 -->\n<view class=\"modal\" wx:if=\"{{ended}}\">\n  <view class=\"modal-box\">\n    <text class=\"modal-title\">{{result}}</text>\n    <button class=\"btn primary\" bindtap=\"restart\">再来一局</button>\n    <button class=\"btn\" bindtap=\"goBack\">返回首页</button>\n  </view>\n</view>\n","path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\WeChatProjects\\wuziqi-game\\miniprogram\\pages\\game\\game.wxml"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_229652bda9c041bb9bfa4d89","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/* game.wxss */\n\npage {\n  height: 100%;\n  background: #1a1a2e;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.game-container {\n  height: 100vh;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n}\n\n.header {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 24rpx 40rpx;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\n}\n\n.player {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 12rpx 24rpx;\n  border-radius: 8rpx;\n}\n\n.player.active {\n  background: rgba(233,69,96,0.2);\n}\n\n.player text {\n  font-size: 28rpx;\n  color: #fff;\n  margin: 0 12rpx;\n}\n\n.chess {\n  width: 36rpx;\n  height: 36rpx;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n}\n\n.chess.black { background: #222; border: 2rpx solid #444; }\n.chess.white { background: #fff; border: 2rpx solid #ccc; }\n\n.vs {\n  font-size: 24rpx;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);\n}\n\n.status {\n  padding: 16rpx;\n  text-align: center;\n  font-size: 26rpx;\n  color: #e94560;\n}\n\n.board-box {\n  flex: 1;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  padding: 20rpx;\n  min-height: 0;\n}\n\n.board-frame {\n  background: #d4a574;\n  border-radius: 8rpx;\n  box-shadow: 0 8rpx 32rpx rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n}\n\n.actions {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  gap: 24rpx;\n  padding: 24rpx 40rpx;\n  padding-bottom: calc(24rpx + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));\n}\n\n.btn {\n  padding: 16rpx 36rpx;\n  font-size: 28rpx;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\n  color: #fff;\n  border-radius: 8rpx;\n}\n\n.btn.primary { background: #e94560; }\n.btn[disabled] { opacity: 0.4; }\n\n/* 弹窗 */\n.modal {\n  position: fixed;\n  inset: 0;\n  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85);\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  z-index: 999;\n}\n\n.modal-box {\n  background: #16213e;\n  padding: 48rpx 64rpx;\n  border-radius: 16rpx;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.modal-title {\n  display: block;\n  font-size: 44rpx;\n  color: #fff;\n  margin-bottom: 32rpx;\n}\n\n.modal-box .btn {\n  display: block;\n  width: 280rpx;\n  margin: 16rpx auto;\n}\n","path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\WeChatProjects\\wuziqi-game\\miniprogram\\pages\\game\\game.wxss"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1027933d7ce0433492c15719","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"// game.js - 五子棋游戏逻辑\n\nconst { checkWin } = require('../../utils/win-check')\nconst { getAIMove } = require('../../utils/ai')\n\nconst SIZE = 15  // 15x15棋盘\n\nPage({\n  data: {\n    mode: 'pvp',\n    currentPlayer: 1,\n    player1Name: '黑棋',\n    player2Name: '白棋',\n    statusText: '黑棋先行',\n    ended: false,\n    result: '',\n    canUndo: false,\n    boardPx: 300,  // 棋盘像素尺寸\n    board: []\n  },\n\n  // 实例变量\n  canvas: null,\n  ctx: null,\n  cellPx: 0,  // 格子像素尺寸\n  history: [],\n\n  onLoad(opt) {\n    this.setData({\n      mode: opt.mode || 'pvp',\n      player2Name: opt.mode === 'pve' ? 'AI' : '白棋'\n    })\n    this.initBoard()\n  },\n\n  onReady() {\n    // 计算棋盘尺寸\n    const sys = wx.getSystemInfoSync()\n    const boardPx = sys.windowWidth - 80  // 留边距\n    \n    this.setData({ boardPx }, () => {\n      // 等待渲染完成\n      setTimeout(() => this.setupCanvas(), 50)\n    })\n  },\n\n  initBoard() {\n    const board = []\n    for (let i = 0; i < SIZE; i++) {\n      board.push(new Array(SIZE).fill(0))\n    }\n    this.setData({\n      board,\n      currentPlayer: 1,\n      ended: false,\n      canUndo: false\n    })\n    this.history = []\n  },\n\n  setupCanvas() {\n    const query = wx.createSelectorQuery()\n    query.select('#board')\n      .fields({ node: true })\n      .exec(res => {\n        if (!res[0]) {\n          console.error('Canvas not found')\n          return\n        }\n        \n        const canvas = res[0].node\n        const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d')\n        const dpr = wx.getSystemInfoSync().pixelRatio\n        const boardPx = this.data.boardPx\n        \n        // 设置Canvas像素尺寸\n        canvas.width = boardPx * dpr\n        canvas.height = boardPx * dpr\n        ctx.scale(dpr, dpr)\n        \n        // 计算格子尺寸\n        this.cellPx = boardPx / SIZE\n        \n        this.canvas = canvas\n        this.ctx = ctx\n        \n        console.log('Canvas ready:', boardPx, 'cellPx:', this.cellPx)\n        \n        this.render()\n      })\n  },\n\n  render() {\n    if (!this.ctx) return\n    \n    const ctx = this.ctx\n    const boardPx = this.data.boardPx\n    const cellPx = this.cellPx\n    \n    // 背景\n    ctx.fillStyle = '#d4a574'\n    ctx.fillRect(0, 0, boardPx, boardPx)\n    \n    // 网格线\n    ctx.strokeStyle = '#8b6914'\n    ctx.lineWidth = 1\n    \n    for (let i = 0; i < SIZE; i++) {\n      const p = i * cellPx + cellPx / 2\n      // 横\n      ctx.beginPath()\n      ctx.moveTo(cellPx / 2, p)\n      ctx.lineTo(boardPx - cellPx / 2, p)\n      ctx.stroke()\n      // 竖\n      ctx.beginPath()\n      ctx.moveTo(p, cellPx / 2)\n      ctx.lineTo(p, boardPx - cellPx / 2)\n      ctx.stroke()\n    }\n    \n    // 星位\n    ctx.fillStyle = '#5c4033'\n    const stars = [[3,3],[3,7],[3,11],[7,3],[7,7],[7,11],[11,3],[11,7],[11,11]]\n    stars.forEach(([r, c]) => {\n      ctx.beginPath()\n      ctx.arc((c + 0.5) * cellPx, (r + 0.5) * cellPx, 3, 0, Math.PI * 2)\n      ctx.fill()\n    })\n    \n    // 棋子\n    const { board } = this.data\n    for (let r = 0; r < SIZE; r++) {\n      for (let c = 0; c < SIZE; c++) {\n        if (board[r][c]) {\n          this.drawPiece(r, c, board[r][c])\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  },\n\n  drawPiece(row, col, player) {\n    const ctx = this.ctx\n    const cellPx = this.cellPx\n    const x = (col + 0.5) * cellPx\n    const y = (row + 0.5) * cellPx\n    const r = cellPx * 0.38\n    \n    // 阴影\n    ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,0.2)'\n    ctx.beginPath()\n    ctx.arc(x + 1, y + 1, r, 0, Math.PI * 2)\n    ctx.fill()\n    \n    // 棋子\n    ctx.fillStyle = player === 1 ? '#222' : '#fff'\n    ctx.beginPath()\n    ctx.arc(x, y, r, 0, Math.PI * 2)\n    ctx.fill()\n    \n    ctx.strokeStyle = player === 1 ? '#000' : '#aaa'\n    ctx.lineWidth = 1\n    ctx.stroke()\n  },\n\n  handleTap(e) {\n    if (this.data.ended) return\n    if (this.data.mode === 'pve' && this.data.currentPlayer === 2) return\n    \n    // 获取相对于Canvas的坐标\n    const { x, y } = e.detail\n    if (!x && !y) return\n    \n    const cellPx = this.cellPx\n    \n    // 计算格子坐标\n    const col = Math.floor(x / cellPx)\n    const row = Math.floor(y / cellPx)\n    \n    console.log('Tap:', x, y, '->', row, col)\n    \n    // 边界检查\n    if (row < 0 || row >= SIZE || col < 0 || col >= SIZE) return\n    if (this.data.board[row][col]) return\n    \n    this.place(row, col)\n  },\n\n  place(row, col) {\n    const { board, currentPlayer } = this.data\n    \n    // 振动\n    wx.vibrateShort({ type: 'light' })\n    \n    // 更新\n    board[row][col] = currentPlayer\n    this.history.push({ row, col, player: currentPlayer })\n    \n    this.setData({ board, canUndo: this.history.length > 0 })\n    this.render()\n    \n    // 胜负\n    if (checkWin(board, row, col, currentPlayer, 5)) {\n      const name = currentPlayer === 1 ? '黑棋' : (this.data.mode === 'pve' ? 'AI' : '白棋')\n      this.setData({ ended: true, result: name + '获胜！' })\n      return\n    }\n    \n    // 平局\n    if (this.history.length >= SIZE * SIZE) {\n      this.setData({ ended: true, result: '平局！' })\n      return\n    }\n    \n    // 换手\n    const next = currentPlayer === 1 ? 2 : 1\n    this.setData({\n      currentPlayer: next,\n      statusText: next === 1 ? '轮到黑棋' : (this.data.mode === 'pve' ? 'AI思考...' : '轮到白棋')\n    })\n    \n    // AI\n    if (this.data.mode === 'pve' && next === 2) {\n      setTimeout(() => this.aiTurn(), 400)\n    }\n  },\n\n  aiTurn() {\n    if (this.data.ended) return\n    const move = getAIMove(this.data.board, SIZE)\n    if (move) this.place(move.row, move.col)\n  },\n\n  undo() {\n    if (!this.history.length) return\n    \n    const { board, mode } = this.data\n    const count = mode === 'pve' && this.history.length >= 2 ? 2 : 1\n    \n    for (let i = 0; i < count; i++) {\n      const last = this.history.pop()\n      board[last.row][last.col] = 0\n    }\n    \n    this.setData({\n      board,\n      canUndo: this.history.length > 0,\n      currentPlayer: this.history.length % 2 === 0 ? 1 : 2\n    })\n    this.render()\n  },\n\n  restart() {\n    this.initBoard()\n    this.render()\n  },\n\n  goBack() {\n    wx.navigateBack()\n  }\n})\n","path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\WeChatProjects\\wuziqi-game\\miniprogram\\pages\\game\\game.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":109305,"output":3335,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112640,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775144971649,"responseId":"28e58d87bde085f0cd7772922e2da7e2"}}
