{"type":"message","id":"0c5f02a1","parentId":"ddbec208","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:51:04.838Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，代码已经重写。这次的改进：\n\n1. 使用 `style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\"` 让Canvas填充父容器\n2. 父容器 `.board-frame` 使用计算的 `boardPx` 设置固定尺寸\n3. Canvas像素尺寸 = boardPx * dpr，确保高清\n4. 格子尺寸 = boardPx / SIZE，确保正方形网格\n5. 使用 `bindtap` 事件，通过 `e.detail.x/y` 获取坐标\n\n让我告诉用户测试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"老板，已重写。主要改进：\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 修复说明\n\n| 问题 | 解决 |\n|------|------|\n| 棋盘闪烁不同步 | 先设置 `boardPx`，再初始化Canvas |\n| 棋盘长方形 | Canvas宽高一致，格子 = boardPx / 15 |\n| 无法落子 | 简化坐标计算，使用 `e.detail.x/y` |\n\n---\n\n## 关键改动\n\n```javascript\n// 1. 先计算棋盘尺寸\nconst boardPx = sys.windowWidth - 80\nthis.setData({ boardPx })\n\n// 2. 再初始化Canvas\ncanvas.width = boardPx * dpr  // 像素尺寸\ncanvas.height = boardPx * dpr  // 宽高一致 = 正方形\n\n// 3. 格子尺寸\nthis.cellPx = boardPx / 15  // 15个格子\n\n// 4. 点击坐标\nconst col = Math.floor(x / cellPx)\nconst row = Math.floor(y / cellPx)\n```\n\n---\n\n**请按 Ctrl+B 重新编译测试。**\n\n如果还有问题，请告诉我控制台打印的日志信息（应该会打印 `Canvas ready: xxx cellPx: xxx` 和 `Tap: xxx xxx -> xxx xxx`）。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":112430,"output":491,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112921,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775145046659,"responseId":"0218d381a9ce23b042f90b6fd206cd06"}}
